description:
Special days mean celebrations!
Barbecue, sushi, pizza, cake~☆
Isn't being able to party together
just the greatest? ♪

It is all thanks to your talents
that we made it to this occasion.
I expected no less, my lord.
What a good boy you are! ♪

Hey, this is actually kind of a big
deal, huh? I guess I'm a little bit...
w-well, okay, a lot impressed.
Keep up the good work! ♪
This celebration is a special time\nfor both of us. You give me the\ncourage to always do my best!

I'd nyever miss out on
celebrating your special occasion.
I'm a huge fan of all the fur-
raising exploits you get up to! ♪

Ahhh, I ate too much shaved ice,
and now my body's freezing!
You'll help me warm up,
won't you? Big hugs~! ♪

One frequently hears that the
summer season is rife with
dangers... But I will protect you
no matter what arises, my lord.

How did I end up spending my
summer with you of all people?
Oh well, I guess it's been fun.
Come on, we're not done yet!

Our very first summer together...
I'm so excited, I might collapse!
I'm sure it'll be another wonderful
experience to remember!

Summer's big for business,
but somehow this year I want to
spend it with you. You're nyot
gonna make me regret it, are ya?
